259
00:22:35,300 --> 00:22:37,350
Properly restored, of course.

260
00:22:37,430 --> 00:22:41,100
Well, his Parma Charnel House
went for six...

261
00:22:41,180 --> 00:22:45,020
But that was 10 years ago,
and it didn't have this moulding.

262
00:22:45,100 --> 00:22:48,190
I see. I can't get enough
