our friend's home!

321
00:26:33,500 --> 00:26:36,170
Well, I bought
a present for ya, buddy.

322
00:26:36,250 --> 00:26:41,340
Ernie, i-it's just a little mouse.
Do we really have to kill it?

323
00:26:41,420 --> 00:26:45,300
