A single vermin can bring you down.

324
00:26:45,390 --> 00:26:48,720
Believe me, I know. (Snap) Ah...

325
00:26:54,940 --> 00:26:56,810
(Snoring)

326
00:27:21,960 --> 00:27:24,050
- (Snap)
- (Gasps)

327
00:27:24,130 --> 00:27:26,760
(Sighs)

328
00:27:34,390 --> 00:27:39,150
- I trust you slept well.
- Oh! Like a baby.

329
00:27:47,700 --> 00:27:50,410
Hey, last night,
did you hear the, uh...

330
