and left the pit just to mock us.

334
00:28:15,640 --> 00:28:19,610
You're giving him
a little too much credit.

335
00:28:19,690 --> 00:28:23,320
Mice don't mock.
They don't have a sense of humour.

336
00:28:23,400 --> 00:28:26,570
He's not sitting in his hole
in a smoking jacket,

337
00:28:26,650 --> 00:28:29,700
sipping cognac,
giggling "I left the pit."

338
00:28:29,780 --> 00:28:33,540
The trap snapped itself,
the olive flew off, and he ate it.

339
00:28:33,620 --> 00:28:37,580
But now he knows we're here,
he won't come near us.

340
00:28:37,660 --> 00:28:40,380
We won't be seeing that... Mouse!

341
00:28:40,460 --> 00:28:42,090
(Both shrieking)

342
00:28:43,420 --> 00:28:45,840
Aha! Ow!

343
00:28:45,920 --> 00:28:47,220
(Screams)

344
00:28:47,300 --> 00:28:50,970
What are you doing, ya stupid nitwit?

345
00:28:53,060 --> 00:28:55,520
Don't let him get away!

346
00:28:59,810 --> 00:29:01,440
