00:29:37,600 --> 00:29:40,310
Get me my Gouda.

356
00:29:42,900 --> 00:29:46,860
- Careful, careful!
- Don't touch me. You'll snap it.

357
00:29:46,940 --> 00:29:49,030
You're not doin' it right.

358
00:29:49,110 --> 00:29:52,030
(Lars) Put it on carefully.
(Ernie) I am.

359
00:29:52,110 --> 00:29:55,160
(Ernie) Oh, relax. It's cheese.

360
00:29:56,580 --> 00:29:58,450
Bon appetit.

361
00:30:00,580 --> 00:30:03,790
That takes care of that. Huh?

362
00:30:09,630 --> 00:30:11,260
(Hammering)

363
00:30:17,060 --> 00:30:18,970
Oh! Oh!

364
00:30:25,730 --> 00:30:27,360
Hey!

365
00:30:28,320 --> 00:30:30,400
Hey! What are you doin'?

366
00:30:33,200 --> 00:30:34,990
(Squeaking)

367
00:32:05,330 --> 00:32:07,290
(Chugging)

368
00:32:16,260 --> 00:32:18,090
(Squeaking)

369
00:32:48,420 --> 00:32:51,170
Lars! Gimme a hand with this.

370
00:32:56,800 --> 00:32:59,590
(Lars) You sure this tub
fits with the house?

371
00:32:59,680 --> 00:33:02,220
Jacuzzi tub, Lars.
It's a Jacuzzi tub.

372
00:33:02,300 --> 00:33:05,060
And this isn't just a house.
It's a LaRue.

373
00:33:05,140 --> 00:33:07,100
Of course it fits the decor.

374
00:33:07,180 --> 00:33:10,350
- Luxury is timeless.
- How much, Ernie?

375
00:33:10,440 --> 00:33:13,520
(Sighs) It was a steal at $1200.

376
00:33:13,610 --> 00:33:15,610
(Lars) $1200?

377
00:33:15,690 --> 00:33:18,200
