403
00:36:58,710 --> 00:37:00,580
You said mice like Gouda.

404
00:37:00,670 --> 00:37:03,840
Not in the morning!
They need fruit for energy.

405
00:37:06,670 --> 00:37:08,930
(Screaming)

406
00:37:09,010 --> 00:37:10,930
(Whimpering)

407
00:37:22,940 --> 00:37:26,570
- (Screaming)
- (Ernie) Oh, no!

408
00:37:34,740 --> 00:37:36,830
Ow! Ow.

409
00:37:36,950 --> 00:37:40,670
(Both grunting and groaning)

410
00:37:47,170 --> 00:37:50,130
- Aah... Ow!
- D-D-D-D-D-D-D.

411
00:37:56,100 --> 00:37:57,930
There he goes!

412
00:38:01,020 --> 00:38:03,690
- Juice!
- Got it!

413
00:38:05,980 --> 00:38:07,940
(Laughing maniacally)

414
00:38:08,030 --> 00:38:10,320
This game is over!

415
00:38:10,400 --> 00:38:12,160
(Cheering and yelling)

416
00:38:17,290 --> 00:38:19,330
(Laughing)

417
00:38:25,460 --> 00:38:27,880
- I think it's working!
- Yeah.

