430
00:39:39,030 --> 00:39:43,830
Oh, wait a minute, there's some
mistake, this house is paid for.

431
00:39:43,910 --> 00:39:46,380
It was, but you borrowed against it.

432
00:39:46,460 --> 00:39:49,840
If you don't pay the $1200,
we repossess it.

433
00:39:49,920 --> 00:39:53,760
- $1200?
- Well, how long do we have?

434
00:39:53,840 --> 00:39:58,970
One week from, uh... five days ago.

435
00:39:59,050 --> 00:40:01,890
(Panting) But, uh, that's two days!

436
00:40:01,970 --> 00:40:04,690
We don't have the time
or energy for this.

437
00:40:04,770 --> 00:40:07,900
We're in the midst
of an extensive renovation.

438
00:40:07,980 --> 00:40:11,480
Looks like you're off
to a great start.

439
00:40:12,940 --> 00:40:16,320
(Lars) Ask your boss for an advance.
Pay him back later.

440
00:40:16,410 --> 00:40:20,450
(Ernie) Couldn't your workers
forfeit their salaries?

441
00:40:20,530 --> 00:40:24,750
If you hadn't spent all our money
on that tub, we might be able to pay.

442
00:40:24,830 --> 00:40:28,210
- It doesn't help to start crying.
- (Shrieking)

443
00:40:28,290 --> 00:40:31,340
No, Fluffy! No!

444
00:40:31,420 --> 00:40:34,210
No! I want my kitty!

445
00:40:34,300 --> 00:40:38,800
No, no, no!

446
00:40:47,140 --> 00:40:49,020
