454
00:41:23,510 --> 00:41:27,890
(Maury) Find the one you want
and I'll spay or neuter it myself.

455
00:41:27,980 --> 00:41:30,770
(Lars) Well, these are all kittens.

456
00:41:30,850 --> 00:41:34,530
