- Here, boy.

482
00:43:00,690 --> 00:43:02,570
(Growling)

483
00:43:06,490 --> 00:43:08,080
(Squeaking)

484
00:43:08,160 --> 00:43:10,500
(Yowling)

485
00:43:12,920 --> 00:43:14,830
